               <head>Amulet</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85004693  " rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>A magical spell. </summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="100r" to="100v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Ḳame῾a</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">קמיע</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A protective amulet. On the lower half in the middle, a reference to the standard magical names (סנוי וכו'), followed by transpositions of מכשפה לא תחיה, etc. On the left, with a design in the shape of a hand, בן פרת יוסף וכו'. On the right, diagrams of the Star of David, inscribed with Shaddai, and other names. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>On the four margins, the text והסיר יהוה ממך כך חלי וכו', etc.  </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
